UNIT 6 – Practical Implications of Standards
Unit Overview

This unit focused on GDPR and other regulatory standards, examining real-world case studies and compliance challenges.

Artefacts

GDPR case study

Pampered Pets status-quo risk assessment

Reflection

Analysing GDPR cases revealed how small procedural failures can lead to major regulatory consequences. This unit strengthened my understanding of legal risk and its integration into broader risk management strategies.

References

ICO (2020). Guide to GDPR.
https://ico.org.uk/for-organisations/guide-to-data-protection

Sørensen, B.T. (2018). Digitalisation: Opportunity or Risk?
